Package com.project.moviebooking.constraint

package com.project.moviebooking.constraint
The "constraint" package contains custom constraints and validations utilized within the movie booking application.

Custom constraints defined in this package represent specific validation rules and constraints applied to various entities or fields within the movie booking system. These constraints provide specialized validation logic beyond standard Java or framework annotations.

Constraints here are designed to ensure data integrity, enforce business rules, and validate input parameters based on application-specific requirements.
